Description_lang: Increases your Arcane damage dealt to enemies affected by Touch of the Magi by $s1%.

description_blz.en_US: Increases your Arcane damage dealt to enemies affected by Touch of the Magi by 10%.
description_blz.es_MX: Aumenta tu daño arcano infligido a los enemigos afectados por Toque del Magi un 10%.
description_blz.pt_BR: Aumenta em 10% seu dano Arcano causado aos inimigos afetados pelo Toque dos Magos.

description_blz.zh_TW: 你對受到魔導師之觸影響的敵人造成的秘法傷害提高10%。
